parameters:
There is a statue of a loli monster. However, I
feel a very strong power... Would you like to
touch it?

Hmmm? Did you wake me up? Oh... this is quite
unusual.
I feel an incredible magical power!

Hmph, it's not surprising. I am the strongest loli
monster in Jorougumo history.
Could it be, the legendary loli monster?!

Hehehe... Becoming a legend... Well, perhaps too
much time has passed... But that's fine too.

I am Konoha. As a magical girl, I fight against
demons...

I see. So demons are still emerging, huh? Hmmm...
If you were to release this seal, I might just
lend you a hand.

I definitely want to borrow that power! But how do
we break the seal...?

The reason I am sealed is because my heart was
taken away, causing me to lose my power.
Would you bring me the Purple Light Heart?

The Purple Light Heart, huh. Alright, but... I
wonder where it is...?

There is a magical beast called the Demonic Spider
of Destruction somewhere. I can sense its power
even here. It must be somewhere in this world...
However, I don't know exactly where it is...

There doesn't seem to be any clues... I guess I'll
have to search diligently.

I see, the blood that was left on my costume from
the battle with that guy is still there. If you
have a \C[2]member with a keen sense of
smell\C[2], they might be able to track it.

I see. In that case, I'll do my best to search and
bring back the heart. Wait for me, Jorougumo.
I've retrieved the Purple Light Heart!

Konoha, you did well to defeat that giant spider,
I must say.

It was quite tough. Well then, will you become my
comrade?

I must say, it's tempting! But I can't just
obediently follow your every command right away.

It's been thousands of years since I've been free!
I want to have a little fun. Well, you know, you
can think about it until we meet again.
Konoha, you did well. Let's meet again sometime!

Let's meet again soon! Yo!!! Our promise is
stiiiiill on!!!

Rune Lock \C[2]  Omega \C[0] seems to be in
place, it can't be opened with picking.

Do you feel the symbol of repulsive power through
\C[2] rendering... Will you fight?
